\c 15
\s Imvuselelo kaAsa
\p
\v 1 UMoya kaNkulunkulu\x + Nani 24.2.\x* wasesehlela phezu kukaAzariya indodana kaOdedi\x + 15.8.\x*.
\v 2 Wasephuma ukuhlangabezana loAsa, wathi kuye: Ngilalela, Asa loJuda wonke loBhenjamini; iN\nd kosi\nd* ilani liselayo. Uba-ke liyidinga, izafunyanwa yini\x + 15.4,15. 34.3. 1 Lan. 28.9. Jer. 29.13. Mat. 7.7.\x*; kodwa uba liyilahla, izalilahla\x + 12.5. 24.20. Dute. 31.17. 1 Kho. 18.18. Ezra 8.22.\x*.
\v 3 Okwensuku ezinengi uIsrayeli wayengelaye uNkulunkulu weqiniso\x + Hos. 3.4.\x*, njalo engelaye umpristi ofundisayo, njalo engelawo umlayo\x + 17.8,9. 35.3. Levi 10.11.\x*.
\v 4 Kodwa ekubandezelweni kwakhe waphendukela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, basebemdinga, wasefunyanwa yibo\x + Dute. 4.29.\x*.
\v 5 Langalezozikhathi kwakungelakuthula kophumayo lakongenayo, ngoba inhlupheko ezinengi zaziphezu kwabo bonke abakhi bamazwe\x + Hlu. 5.6.\x*.
\v 6 Basebephahlazwa, isizwe ngesizwe, lomuzi ngomuzi, ngoba uNkulunkulu wabahlupha ngayo yonke imbandezelo.
\v 7 Ngakho lina qinani\x + Josh. 1.6,7,9.\x*, zingadangali izandla zenu\x + 2 Sam. 17.2. Ezra 4.4.\x*, ngoba kulomvuzo ngomsebenzi wenu\x + Gen. 15.1. Hlab. 62.12.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Lapho uAsa esizwa lamazwi lesiprofetho sikaOdedi umprofethi, waziqinisa\x + 15.8.\x*, wasusa izinengiso elizweni lonke lakoJuda loBhenjamini\x + 1 Kho. 15.12.\x* lemizini ayeyithumbile entabeni yakoEfrayimi\x + 17.2. 19.4. 13.19.\x*, wavuselela ilathi leN\nd kosi\nd* elalingaphambi kwekhulusi leN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 8.12.\x*.
\v 9 Wasebuthanisa wonke uJuda loBhenjamini labemzini labo ababevela koEfrayimi loManase lakoSimeyoni; ngoba bawelela kuye bevela koIsrayeli ngobunengi lapho bebona ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakhe yayilaye\x + 11.16. 16.1.\x*.
\v 10 Basebebuthana eJerusalema ngenyanga yesithathu ngomnyaka wetshumi lanhlanu wokubusa kukaAsa\x + Dute. 16.9. Eks. 12.18.\x*.
\v 11 Basebehlabela iN\nd kosi\nd* ngalolosuku okwempango ababe\add yi\add*lethile, inkabi ezingamakhulu ayisikhombisa lezimvu ezizinkulungwane eziyisikhombisa\x + 14.13,15.\x*.
\v 12 Basebengena esivumelwaneni sokudinga iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu waboyise, ngenhliziyo yabo yonke langomphefumulo wabo wonke\x + 29.10. 34.31. 2 Kho. 23.3. Neh. 10.29.\x*.
\v 13 Njalo wonke ongadingi iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli uzabulawa, kusukela komncinyane kusiya komkhulu, kusukela kowesilisa kusiya kowesifazana\x + Dute. 13.9.\x*.
\v 14 Basebefunga eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ngelizwi elikhulu langokumemeza langezimpondo langempondo zezinqama\x + 1 Lan. 15.28. Hlab. 98.6. Hos. 5.8.\x*.
\v 15 AbakoJuda bonke bathokoza-ke ngesifungo, ngoba babefungile ngenhliziyo yabo yonke, beyidingile ngaso sonke isifiso sabo\x + 15.4,15. 34.3. 1 Lan. 28.9. Jer. 29.13. Mat. 7.7.\x*, yasifunyanwa yibo\x + 15.4,15. 34.3. 1 Lan. 28.9. Jer. 29.13. Mat. 7.7.\x*; ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* yabaphumuza inhlangothi zonke\x + 14.7. 20.30.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Njalo mayelana loMahaka unina kaAsa inkosi, yamsusa ekubeni yindlovukazi, ngoba wayenzele isixuku into enengekayo\x + 1 Kho. 15.13-15.\x*. UAsa wasegamula into yakhe enengekayo, wayichola, wayitshisela esifuleni iKidroni\x + 30.14. 2 Kho. 23.6,15.\x*.
\v 17 Kanti indawo eziphakemeyo kazisuswanga koIsrayeli; lanxa kunjalo inhliziyo kaAsa yayiphelele insuku zakhe zonke\x + 14.3,5.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Wasengenisa endlini kaNkulunkulu izinto ezingcwele zikayise, lezinto zakhe ezingcwele, isiliva legolide lezitsha.
\v 19 Kakusabanga khona impi kwaze kwaba ngumnyaka wamatshumi amathathu lanhlanu wokubusa kukaAsa.
